interface.name: similarity
interface.title: Listen to the reference, and then rate how similar each voice is to it

surveystatement.name: sim_instructions
surveystatement.statement:
In part 2 of the survey, you are rating similarity between a reference voice, and all other voice samples. Two voices are similar if you think they are from the same person.
Note that the speech samples are now saying different things.
There are 8 pages in total. On each page: 1. Listen to the reference voice at the top of the page 2. Then listen to the voice samples at the bottom of the page and rate how similar each one is to the reference 3. This is a subjective test, so use your gut instinct when rating. 'Very Similar' means you think the sample voice and the reference voice are from the same person, while 'Very Dissimilar' represents two different voices. 4. Please listen to each speech sample fully

surveystatement.name: sim_reminder
surveystatement.statement: Remember to listen to the reference voice first at the top of the page.
